haxel.HxlList

type
class
The world's smallest linked list class. Useful for optimizing time-critical or highly repetitive tasks! See HxlQuadTree for how to use it, IF YOU DARE.

Constructor

public new()
Creates a new link, and sets object and next to null.

Instance Variables

public next : HxlList

Stores a reference to the next link in the list.

public object : HxlObject

Stores a reference to a HxlObject.
